                            <div class="grid_box size_16 trusted lined">
                                <h2></h2>
                                <p>	<img src="/images.v2/logos.gif" /></p></div>
                            <div id="tabs">
                                <ul><li><a href="#first">About Verotel</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#second">High-risk webmasters</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#third">Providers of Online Services</a></li>
                                </ul><div id="first">
                                <div class="grid_box size_9">
                                    <h2>Trust in global payments since 1998
                                    </h2><p>Verotel is a leading Internet Payment Service Provider (IPSP) since 1998 and is specialized in online credit card payment processing.
Servicing over 50.000 online businesses with online payment solutions, Verotel understands the risks of online billing.</p>
                                    <p>Verotel is the first high risk payment processor awarded with the official Payment Institute status. Processing all major credit cards and offering a fully PCI compliant solution, Verotel is the most trusted online payment processor in the business. High Risk or Online Services? Apply for a Verotel account and get started today.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid_box size_7 usps">
                                    <h2>Company History</h2>
                                    <ul class="usp"><li><span class="red">1998</span> - Verotel processed its first transaction on January 15th 1998</li>
                                        <li><span class="red">2005</span> - PCI was introduced. Verotel became PCI DSS Compliant</li>
                                        <li><span class="red">2011</span> - Verotel was licensed as Payment Institute by Dutch Central Bank</li>
                                        <li><span class="red">2012</span> - Verotel became Payment Facilitator with MasterCard and VISA Merchant Agent</li>
                                        <li><span class="red">2014</span> - Verotel accepts Bitcoin and starts processing for Online Services</li>
                                    </ul></div>
                            </div>
                                <div id="second">
                                    <div class="grid_box size_9">
                                        <h2>High-risk webmasters
                                        </h2><p>Verotel is a leading Internet Payment Service Provider (IPSP) that has been enabling high-risk webmasters with building their online businesses since 1998. Verotel understands the risks involved in supplying digital content and other online services and provides a PCI compliant solution. The money you process is safe with us. Verotel is a registered Payment Institute with the Dutch Central Bank and acts as an executive board member in the European Payment Institutions Federation.</p>
                                        <p><a class="btn apply" href="price-and-comparison-chart.html">Apply today!</a>
                                        </p></div>
                                    <div class="grid_box size_7 usps">
                                        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
                                            <img src="/images.v2/icon-percentage.gif" /></td>
                                            <td>
                                                <p>Competitive rates and high volume discounts.</p>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr><tr><td>
                                            <img src="/images.v2/icon-control.gif" /></td>
                                            <td>
                                                <p>Verotel Control Center: review your sales and manage your accounts with our free easy-to-use dashboard. </p>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr><tr><td>
                                            <img src="/images.v2/icon-support.gif" /></td>
                                            <td>
                                                <p>Specialized cardholder support for online (credit card) transactions.</p>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr></table></div>
                                </div>
                                <div id="third">
                                    <div class="grid_box size_9">
                                        <h2>Online services
                                        </h2><p>Verotel offers Subscription Billing for Online Services, where Verotel knows what it takes to bill weekly, monthly, or at any other interval.</p>
                                        <p>Online service providers sell services such as SaaS, hosting, domains, servers, certificates or any other type of service that is provided online. </p>
                                        <p>Verotel has developed various modules for hosting panels that are used in the hosting industry. These hosting modules allow you to quickly integrate Verotel to sell your Online Services. We even create custom modules when needed.</p>
                                        <p><a class="btn apply" href="apply-for-hosting">Apply today!</a>
                                        </p></div>
                                    <div class="grid_box size_7 usps">
                                        <p>Verotel offers an all-in-one solution, where there is no need to apply for an account with a bank. With our Payment Institute license and Payment Facilitator status you will be processing all major credit cards in no time. You will get:</p>
                                        <ul class="usp"><li>a flexible Verotel account with great rates</li>
                                            <li>integration with most hosting panels</li>
                                            <li>an easy and affordable setup procedure</li>
                                        </ul></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
